history.proof: unfold Sup_seq. qsimpl time: 1 use: is_sup_seq_unique.

exceptions.exn: In environment u : nat -> Rbar Unable to unify "Sup_seq ?M2363 = ?M2364" with "match proj1_sig (ex_sup_seq u) with | Finite l => forall eps : posreal, (forall n : nat, Rbar_lt (u n) (l + eps)) /\\ (exists n : nat, Rbar_lt (l - eps) (u n)) | p_infty => forall M : R, exists n : nat, Rbar_lt M (u n) | m_infty => forall (M : R) (n : nat), Rbar_lt (u n) M end".

original: unfold Sup_seq. apply is_sup_seq_unique. destruct (ex_sup_seq u) as [l Hl]. apply Hl.
